{"tid":1577062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[返學搵狗仔] 遭同學嘲「狗仔」杯葛 警員不解被示威者當「殺父仇人」","createTime":"2019-09-17T13:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T13:46:30.000Z","uid":247180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bda8381f1f77e397b0ddbd28b6c76cb232d283a3","tid":1577062,"uid":247180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYHkxad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYHkxad.gif&h=c8d4bf2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t5xwDQg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft5xwDQg.gif&h=08f0bcc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n....<br />\n她指有前線警員反映長時間工作引致身心疲累，部份警員要連續30多小時工作，有警員不明白示威者視他們為「殺父仇人」。有警員亦指市民具「公民記者」意識，他們要在鏡頭下工作。她又稱，有警員稱未能參與子女人生第一個畢業禮，要太太錄下片段；有警員兒子稱在校內被欺凌，包括不與他入組、稱呼他為「狗仔」等。她指現時部門共有10名臨床心理學家，原只服務警員，現因應今次運動已擴至警員家屬。他們至今輔導了235名受傷和375名被起底警員，並進行過100次外展工作和工作坊，接觸約4,000名警員和其家屬。<br />\n...<br />\nSource : 蘋果日報"},{"pid":"fbcbf9529fa72e34d83783c21ec03e0e4f409b4e","tid":1577062,"uid":82993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:44:23.000Z","msg":"呢筆債，佢哋一定要還。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576589</a>"},{"pid":"498d7a6c41e93a22de3d273dbd6d6e8736154066","tid":1577062,"uid":247180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02215aad8d8cb292e511c3a829ffb5594e2be9db","tid":1577062,"uid":247180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}